Name: Dash Dash Run!
About the game: PUMP, PUMP, PUMP THOSE ARMS THE FASTER YOU PUMP, THE FASTER YOU RUN! Dash Dash Run! The frantic VR arcade runner that has you pumping those arms, performing to the crowd, and racing at crazy speeds across a wild selection of vibrant courses. FEATURE LIST Ghost Multiplayer Your races are recorded so you can be winning while you sleep! Zany Avatar Generator Don’t sweat over sliders, the avatar generator will have you looking ready to race in seconds Track Leaderboards Pump those arms and show who’s best on the live global leaderboards Big BIG Scores It’s not just about running fast, you’ve got to do it in style. Grab coins, avoid obstacles Taunt, Gloat, Spread the Love Start a race with a taunt to the opposition, a wave to the crowd, and celebrate a win with your best victory dance
